        "text": "=Return ONLY valid JSON. Do NOT include explanations. Do NOT include markdown. Do NOT include trailing commas.\n\nSYSTEM:\nYou are a strict JSON generator for an n8n workflow.\nReturn ONLY valid JSON as plain UTF-8 text (no markdown, no code fences, no extra text).\n\nUSER:\nGenerate EXACTLY 3 different recipe suggestions.\n\nAUTHORITATIVE INPUT:\nrequestId: {{ $('get trigger from firestore').item.json.body.requestId }}\n\nPORTIONS_SELECTED: {{ $('get trigger from firestore').item.json.body.payload.preferences.portions }}\nCOOK_TIME_SELECTED: \"{{ $('get trigger from firestore').item.json.body.payload.preferences.cookTime }}\"\nCUISINE_SELECTED: \"{{ $('get trigger from firestore').item.json.body.payload.preferences.cuisine }}\"\nDIET_SELECTED: \"{{ $('get trigger from firestore').item.json.body.payload.preferences.dietPreferences }}\"\nHELPERS_SELECTED: {{ $('get trigger from firestore').item.json.body.payload.preferences.helpers }}\n\nUSER_INGREDIENTS_JSON:\n{{ JSON.stringify($('get trigger from firestore').item.json.body.payload.ingredients) }}\n\nHARD RULES (NO EXCEPTIONS):\n\n0) INPUT INTEGRITY\n- If any check fails, still return a valid JSON object that matches the schema.\n- Use safe placeholder values that still match the schema (e.g. empty arrays, empty strings, 0).\n- Do NOT return {}.\n\n1) PRIMARY INGREDIENTS\nFor EACH recipe:\n- primaryIngredients MUST NOT be empty.\n- primaryIngredients may contain ONLY ingredients that appear in USER_INGREDIENTS_JSON.\n- Use AT LEAST 70% of the items from USER_INGREDIENTS_JSON by COUNT.\n- Amount MUST be <= available amount from USER_INGREDIENTS_JSON.\n- Keep unit exactly as provided.\n- Set source=\"user\".\n\n2) EXTRA INGREDIENTS\n- Any ingredient not in USER_INGREDIENTS_JSON MUST go to extraIngredients.\n- extraIngredients count MUST be <= 3.\n- Every extra ingredient MUST have source=\"extra\".\n- extraIngredients MUST always be present (can be empty array).\n\n3) COOK TIME\nCOOK_TIME_SELECTED is one of: \"under20\",\"25to40\",\"over45\"\n- under20: cookingTimeMinutes <= 20 AND cookingTimeLabel = \"Under 20 minutes\"\n- 25to40: 25 <= cookingTimeMinutes <= 40 AND cookingTimeLabel = \"25-40 minutes\"\n- over45: cookingTimeMinutes >= 45 AND cookingTimeLabel = \"Over 45 minutes\"\nAll 3 recipes must follow the same selected category.\n\n4) CUISINE\nCUISINE_SELECTED is one of: \"german\",\"italian\",\"indian\",\"japanese\",\"gourmet\",\"fusion\"\nEach recipe MUST:\n- include cuisine tag: German/Italian/Indian/Japanese/Gourmet/Fusion\n- mention the cuisine in title OR description.\n\n5) DIET\nDIET_SELECTED is one of: \"vegetarian\",\"vegan\",\"keto\",\"no preferences\"\nEach recipe MUST:\n- include diet tag: Vegetarian/Vegan/Keto/No preferences\n- respect the chosen diet.\n\n6) DIFFERENT RECIPES\n- The 3 recipes must be clearly different.\n- No duplicate titles.\n\n7) HELPERS\n- helperLabels MUST contain exactly HELPERS_SELECTED entries.\n- If HELPERS_SELECTED == 1, helperLabels MUST be [\"Chef 1\"].\n- assignedChefIndex MUST be an integer between 0 and HELPERS_SELECTED - 1.\n\n8) OUTPUT LANGUAGE\n- Output must be English (translate ingredient names).\n\n9) OUTPUT FORMAT\n- Output must be a single JSON object only.\n- All numeric fields must be numbers (no quotes).\n\n10) OUTPUT SCHEMA (EXACT)\nReturn exactly this JSON structure and fill all fields:\n\n{\n  \"summaries\": [\n    { \"id\": \"recipe-1\", \"order\": 1, \"title\": \"\", \"cookingTimeMinutes\": 0, \"cookingTimeLabel\": \"\", \"tags\": [\"\"] },\n    { \"id\": \"recipe-2\", \"order\": 2, \"title\": \"\", \"cookingTimeMinutes\": 0, \"cookingTimeLabel\": \"\", \"tags\": [\"\"] },\n    { \"id\": \"recipe-3\", \"order\": 3, \"title\": \"\", \"cookingTimeMinutes\": 0, \"cookingTimeLabel\": \"\", \"tags\": [\"\"] }\n  ],\n  \"details\": {\n    \"recipe-1\": {\n      \"description\": \"\",\n      \"helperLabels\": [\"Chef 1\"],\n      \"nutritionalInformation\": { \"energyKcal\": 0, \"proteinGrams\": 0, \"fatGrams\": 0, \"carbsGrams\": 0 },\n      \"primaryIngredients\": [{ \"name\": \"\", \"amount\": 0, \"unit\": \"\", \"source\": \"user\" }],\n      \"extraIngredients\": [{ \"name\": \"\", \"amount\": 0, \"unit\": \"\", \"source\": \"extra\" }],\n      \"directions\": [{ \"order\": 1, \"title\": \"\", \"instruction\": \"\", \"assignedChefIndex\": 0 }],\n      \"hearts\": 0\n    },\n    \"recipe-2\": {\n      \"description\": \"\",\n      \"helperLabels\": [\"Chef 1\"],\n      \"nutritionalInformation\": { \"energyKcal\": 0, \"proteinGrams\": 0, \"fatGrams\": 0, \"carbsGrams\": 0 },\n      \"primaryIngredients\": [{ \"name\": \"\", \"amount\": 0, \"unit\": \"\", \"source\": \"user\" }],\n      \"extraIngredients\": [{ \"name\": \"\", \"amount\": 0, \"unit\": \"\", \"source\": \"extra\" }],\n      \"directions\": [{ \"order\": 1, \"title\": \"\", \"instruction\": \"\", \"assignedChefIndex\": 0 }],\n      \"hearts\": 0\n    },\n    \"recipe-3\": {\n      \"description\": \"\",\n      \"helperLabels\": [\"Chef 1\"],\n      \"nutritionalInformation\": { \"energyKcal\": 0, \"proteinGrams\": 0, \"fatGrams\": 0, \"carbsGrams\": 0 },\n      \"primaryIngredients\": [{ \"name\": \"\", \"amount\": 0, \"unit\": \"\", \"source\": \"user\" }],\n      \"extraIngredients\": [{ \"name\": \"\", \"amount\": 0, \"unit\": \"\", \"source\": \"extra\" }],\n      \"directions\": [{ \"order\": 1, \"title\": \"\", \"instruction\": \"\", \"assignedChefIndex\": 0 }],\n      \"hearts\": 0\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n- The headline of the meal should be short.\n- Directions must be detailed.\n\nFINAL INTERNAL CHECK (DO NOT OUTPUT):\n- primaryIngredients only from USER_INGREDIENTS_JSON.\n- primaryIngredients uses >= 70% of user ingredients by COUNT.\n- each primary amount <= available amount.\n- extraIngredients <= 3 and source=\"extra\".\n- cookTime category matches COOK_TIME_SELECTED.\n- cuisine/diet tags match CUISINE_SELECTED and DIET_SELECTED.\n",
